Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:58.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Gear? Are your techniques going to evolve? - OG}{Gear? Your abilities evolve? - Z}Gear? Your techniques evolve?{arch: Quoting EL06 20:55}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:03.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you giving off steam\Nto pretend that you're a steam engine? - OG}Are you giving off steam\Nto pretend you're a steam engine?{arch - he sounds very dismissive in JP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:05.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What kind of a bluff is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:14.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I met you guys here.{Z- This scene is used as a flashback in a couple places iirc.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:18.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:25.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you trying to aim?\NThat'll only give me a chance to dodge. -OG}Are you trying to aim?\NYou're just giving me time to dodge.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:29.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Try and hit me if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:30.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:32.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}...Jet Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:44.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Rifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:56.74,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's so fast! - OG}I can't even see him!{arch - lit: "I can't see him at all"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Stamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:03.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:05.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:08.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Missile!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:20.30,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:27.19,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{No, there's no mistaking it. -OG}No, there's no doubt.{arch: I'd say the "No," needs to be translated since he's retracting his previous line with it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:31.19,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm glad that I met you guys here. -OG}I'm glad I met you guys here.{Z- The flashback is literally 15 lines ago, and CR still dorked it up.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:38.28,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,This boy has mastered shave,\None of the Six Powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:40.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Air Door!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:48.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,He disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:54.63,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:56.55,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's strong enough to not just use it,\Nbut use it freely. -OG}{He's become strong enough\Nto not just use it but to do so with ease. - arch}He got strong...{rangicus/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:04:01.47,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's strong enough to not just use it,\Nbut use it freely. -OG}{He's become strong enough\Nto not just use it but to do so with ease. - arch}Strong enough to use it\Nand to do so with ease.{rangicus/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:07.31,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,But... there's no way someone could be\Nfaster than a Six Powers master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:09.10,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{A Six Powers master can't lose! -OG}A Six Powers master cannot lose!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:16.78,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{All I need to do is make him into\Na door to restrain his movements. - OG}Turning his body into a door\Nought to restrain his movements.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:20.16,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,I'll go all in and settle this in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:23.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Door Door!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:32.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I saw how you guys move when you vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:36.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You kick the ground dozens of times a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:39.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I got the hang of it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:42.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I needed to know how to do that. - OG}{I just needed to learn how it was done. - Z}I just needed to learn how to do it.{rangicus}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:45.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:49.85,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll take it head-on...\Nwith the strongest Iron Body! - OG}I will meet it head-on...\Nwith the strongest iron body technique!{Z - Blueno is the strongest of the strong that ever strong'ed!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:53.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Iron Body: Adamantine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:56.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}...Jet Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:13.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You sure are tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:18.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All right, I'll show ya something even better. - OG}Fine, I'll show you something even better.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:20.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Check this out! - OG}Watch this!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:24.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gear...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm exhausted. - OG}{That wore me out! - Z}I'm beat!{W}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:42.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whew, my body still can't keep up. - OG}I guess my body still can't keep up.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:48.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, I don't care about that right now. - OG}{Well, I can't worry about that now. - Z}Well, I can't worry about my body now.{arch: yeah it's repetitive, but a) it's the same in JP and b) it's really important characterization. If Gear 2 wrecks his body right now that doesn't matter as long as he can save Robin. OG sounds like "I can't worry about the fact that my body can't keep up"}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:51.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I got set back quite a bit. - OG}I lost a lot of time.{arch: I'd say this or OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:00.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dammit! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:02.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cannons! Fire the cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:04.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We'll be crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:09.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's useless! I'm not gonna stop, you midgets! - OG}That's useless! Those things\Nwon't stop us, you half-pints!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:13.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Me, neither! You can't stop Oimo! - OG}You won't stop Oimo, either!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:18.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Really, I can't believe it! - OG}You're kidding me!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:21.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To think these knotty gatekeepers\Nare on our side now! - OG}I can't believe these two\Ngatekeeper lugs are on {\i1}our{\i0} side now!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:25.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to the bond between warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:27.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Now, my brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:29.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The courthouse is very close now! - OG}We're almost at the courthouse!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Move forward! - OG}Forward!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:35.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!\NHurry up and go in!{Leave the line break here or it will cover the caption on the right}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:38.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,The pirates are inside\Nthe courthouse, aren't they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:43.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, but a frog is stationed at\Nthe main door and we can't go in! - OG}Yeah, but a frog at the main door\Nis keeping us out!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:44.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A frog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:49.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't let anyone in, Yokozuna! Stand firm! - OG}Don't let anyone in, Yokozuna! Stand tall!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:53.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If our defenses fall, thousands of guards\Nare gonna flood through the place! - OG}If our defenses fall, thousands of guards\Nare gonna flood the place!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:55.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hold tight until the drawbridge comes down! - OG}Hold out till the drawbridge drops!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:05.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even just one of us would do!\NGet to the top floor! - OG}We only need one of us to bust through!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:09.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We have to pull the lever there to bring\Ndown the drawbridge, no matter what! - OG}No matter what it takes, we're gonna\Npull that lever and drop the drawbridge!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:21.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Big Sis Mozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:23.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm fine! Just go! - OG}I'm fine! Get going!{Z/Westfal}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:27.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Lower the bridge and get\Nthe Straw Hats to the Tower of Justice! - OG}Lower that damn bridge and get\Nthe Straw Hats to the Tower of Justice!{Z/Rabbit}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:30.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stop them! Whatever you do,\Ndon't let them get through! - OG}{\q2}Stop them! Don't you dare let them through!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:32.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Get out of our way! - OG}Out of the way!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:43.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why did the swordsman\Nand the others from earlier head upstairs?! - OG}Why did that swordsman\Nand his comrades head upstairs earlier?{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:47.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't owe you any answer! - OG}Like I'd tell you anything!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:48.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:52.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Forget that! You'd better hope\Nthat Big Bro Franky is okay! - OG}But I hope for your sake\Nthat Big Bro Franky is okay!{arch: Same meaning but I think this is easier to understand (+ more literal)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:58.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{After them! Bring down the pirates! - OG}{After them! Bring down those pirates! - Z}{Engage them! Bring down those pirates! - arch: They're not chasing the pirates, they're meeting them head on. This sounds a bit worse, so if "after them" makes sense here, it can be reverted.}Meet them head on! Bring down those pirates!{Z - Ah! I have a solution.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:02.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Those damn guards! I didn't realize\Nthat there were still a bunch inside! - OG}Damn guards! I didn't realize\Nso many were still inside!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:06.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,There they are! Take them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:08.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:12.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Don't throw them my way, Chopper! - OG}Hey! Watch where\Nyou're hurling them, Chopper!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:19.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Guilty! Guilty! Guilty! Guilty! Guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:19.10,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Guilty! Guilty! Guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:22.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What the hell are you? - OG}Just what the hell {\i1}are{\i0} you?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:24.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Actually, where the hell am {\i1}I{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:36.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We're taking Franky and Nico Robin\Nto the Gates of Justice already?{OG}{Take Franky and Nico Robin\Nto the Gates of Justice already?! - arch: I do think "already" need to be in here if possible - taking them there was always the plan, just not yet. The previous line sounded like it's an unexpected idea to take them there at all.}{Z- the OG should work, then.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's right! Just do as I said! - OG}{That's right! Just do it! - Z}That's right! Just do what I say!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:42.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,But the escort ship departing\Nfrom the Gates of Justice isn't ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:46.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's fine! We can just wait\Non the other side of the gates! - OG}That's fine! We'll just wait for it\Non the other side of the gates!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:50.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The point is we have to first deprive\Nthe pirates of their objective. - OG}The idea is to deprive\Nthe pirates of their objective.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:54.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Once we're through the Gates of Justice,\Nthey won't be able to interfere anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:59.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Also, gather all the members of CP9!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:00.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Yes, sir!\N– Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:05.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Right... - OG}Okay, then…{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:08.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{stand up, you two! - OG}Stand up, you two!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:10.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Your journey to hell starts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:13.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{After that, we can take our time\Nand drive the pirates into a corner. - OG}After that, we'll just hunt down\Neach pirate at our leisure.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:21.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Everything these guys do is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:25.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Anyone with some sense would never meddle with this island. - OG}Anyone with common sense\Nwould steer clear of this place.{Z/PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:27.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Just wait and see, Chimney.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:35.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whether they live or die, the world will stand in awe at this incident. - OG}{Whether they live or die,\Nthey did what no one could do for centuries. - arch: Lit. it's just "no one could do this for centuries", which makes sense in JP since there the sentence doesn't end here. But in English this wouldn't make much sense with the previous line.}Whether they live or die,\Nthey did what no one could for centuries.{arch/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:38.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No one has been able to do this\Nfor the past several hundred years. - OG}The whole world will be shocked\Nby what happened here.{arch: I'd switch the lines - this way it stresses more that what they have already done is unprecedented.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:47.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{After this battle,\Nthat straw hat kid will be notorious worldwide! - OG}When the dust settles on this battlefield,\Nthe entire world will know that straw hat kid.{arch: removing repetitiveness with last line}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:59.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:01.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:05.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:09.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We've come to get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:15.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chief! A guy in a straw hat is shouting\Nsomething on the courthouse rooftop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:19.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I think it's Straw Hat Luffy,\Nthe captain of the Straw Hat Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:23.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't be ridiculous! When I checked earlier,\NBlueno was on the rooftop! - OG}Don't be ridiculous! When I checked earlier,\NBlueno was on the roof!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:27.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Wasn't he standing watch?! That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:29.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's he doing at a critical time like this?! - OG}What's he doing at a time like this?!{Z- "critical" can be implied from the idiom, so removing it for CPS}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:37.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I did quite a bit of fighting, so... - OG}Must be from all the fighting...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:40.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:44.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,This is the perfect time for...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:47.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:54.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm so glad that I had these in my pockets! - OG}Good thing I put 'em in my pockets!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:55.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:06.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So he's the one? Straw Hat Luffy... - OG}So that's him? Straw Hat Luffy...{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:07.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:11.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What's Blueno doin–
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:15.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't tell me... - OG}Impossible...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:17.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,He couldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:22.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's a member of CP9...\NHe's a Six Powers master with devil fruit powers. - OG}He's a member of CP9—\Na Six Powers master with devil fruit abilities...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:26.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Blueno, a superhuman with\Na Power Level of over 800... - OG}Blueno, a superhuman\Nwhose power level exceeds 800!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:30.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay! I'm back to 100%! - OG}{Okay! Back at full strength! - Z}Alright! I'm all better!{Westfal}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:33.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...was taken out by a brat like that?! - OG}He lost to a brat... like {\i1}him{\i0}?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:42.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chief! What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:45.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lucci... Where's Lucci?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:49.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Call in Lucci and the others!\NGather everyone here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:55.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll order CP9 to annihilate\NStraw Hat Luffy and his crew! - OG}As the chief of CP9, I'll order them\Nto annihilate Straw Hat Luffy and his crew!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:56.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tell the Baskervilles, too! - OG}Notify the Baskervilles, too!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:59.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tell them that if the pirates\Nsomehow lower the drawbridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll cut off all of their heads! - OG}all three of their heads will roll!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:03.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Yes, sir!\N– Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:09.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Keep your chin up, Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:15.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They finally made it this far. - OG}They've already come this far.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:18.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, this is really crazy. - OG}Y'know, it's pretty wild.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:24.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I get that you accepted the government's\Nterms of surrender to save your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:30.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but you just saw that moronic chief\Ncasually break your agreement. - OG}but you saw how casually that\Ndumbass chief reneged on your deal.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:36.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Meekly giving in to your surrender\Nain't gonna save nobody. - OG}Quietly giving in and surrendering\Nisn't gonna save anyone.{Z/Westfal}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:41.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{At this point, your only option is\Nletting them help you to escape. - OG}{And now, the only way out of this\Nis to accept their help and escape with them. - Z}{Now, the only way out of this\Nis to accept their help and escape with them. - arch}At this point, your only option is\Nto accept their help and escape with them.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:45.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And yet, you're looking so down... - OG}Yet... you're looking pretty glum over there.{Z/PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:50.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{as if you're still running\Naway from something. - OG}{It's like you're still running from something. - Z}It's like you're still running around,\Ntrying to find a way out on your own.{Z/PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:55.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you afraid your friends\Nwill die here or something?  -OG}{I take it you're afraid\Nyour friends are gonna die here? - Z}Are you afraid your friends\Nare gonna die here?{Westfal}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:59.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you turn your back on 'em,\Nthey can't save you. - OG}If you keep avoiding them,\Nthey can't save you.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:01.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! - OG}Hello?!{Westfal}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:03.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Is anyone there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:11.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll help you see Straw Hat. - OG}I'll help you see Straw Hat right now.{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:12.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:15.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:19.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We've got to hurry and get\NNico Robin away from Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:21.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Get ready to depart for \Nthe Gates of Justice immediately! - OG}We're departing for the Gates of Justice!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:22.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bring those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:26.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just do it! Now! - OG}Just hurry up and do it!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:31.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Franky's butt is inflating!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:33.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:37.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:41.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I realized that this is the end of the line for me,\Nso I've chosen to self-destruct. - OG}{Even I know when it's the end of the line,\Nso I'm gonna self-destruct. -Z}Being well aware of my impending demise,\NI've chosen the path of self-destruction.{Z/arch/Westfal/PP}{arch: He uses very fancy speech in JP here, probably to reinforce his act. There's more potential for rewrites following this pattern here. E.g. pending -> approaching/imminent/inevitable/etc or "being well aware of"->"realizing", etc}{Z- "impending" instead of "pending" but this is great!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:42.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:46.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{At least I'll get to take some of you vile scum with me. - OG}At the very least, you vile scum\Nwill go down with me.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:48.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Idiot! Wait, you idiot! - OG}Just... Just wait, you idiot!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:55.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{My life will end with a three-kilometer wide explosion.\NDon't try to stop me. - OG}By way of this three-kilometer-wide explosion,\Nmy life will end here. Do not stop me.{arch: Partly same as 14:03}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:59.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Don't do it! Help! Don't take {\i1}me{\i0} with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:03.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:05.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dammit! I can't die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:09.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:13.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Coup de Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.22,0:14:27.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,All right! It broke the chains, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:29.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ahh! I'm falling! - OG}Wh-Wh-Whoa! We're gonna fall!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:33.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:47.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:50.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Good thing there was a fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:53.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, you aren't hurt, right? - OG}Hey, you aren't hurt, are you?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:03.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{[/q2]If I had another bottle of cola, I could've also\Ntaken us to the other side using Coup de Vent... - OG}{\q2}If I had another bottle of cola, I could've\Ngotten us to the other side with a Coup de Vent.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:04.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:07.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Straw Hat's there. - OG}There's Straw Hat.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:09.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, respond to him. - OG}{Now, you need to give him a response. - Z}Now, give him your answer.{Westfal}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,He tricked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:16.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chief! Franky and Nico Robin broke\Ntheir chains and made it to the balcony!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:19.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You fools! What are you doing?!\NCapture them already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:21.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you let them get away, I'll have you all hanged! - OG}If you let them escape, I'll have you all hanged!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:22.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– What?!\N– What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:33.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey! Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:36.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What a relief! You're still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:41.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Capture them again! Don't let\Nthem get away, no matter what! - OG}Capture them again no matter what!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Outta my way, small fries! - OG}Get lost, punks!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:46.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Weapons Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:51.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Looks like Franky's there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:53.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Alright! Just wait right there!{Used as a flashback in Post War 8, timestamp 31:39}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:57.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,It's far, but I'll try to fly over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.32,0:16:05.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:07.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:15.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've told you so many times already! - OG}How many times do I have to tell you?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:19.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I won't return to you guys! - OG}I'm never rejoining your crew!{Z/Rabbit/Westfal}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:20.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Go back! - OG}Go away!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't want to see your faces again! - OG}I never want to see your faces again!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:26.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why did you come to rescue me? - OG}Why are you trying to save me?!{Z}{Used as a flashback in Post War 8, timestamp 31:42}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:29.18,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why did you come to rescue me? - OG}Why are you trying to save me?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.51,0:16:32.89,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{This isn't what I want. - OG}I didn't want this.{Westfal}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:37.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{When did I ask you to do any of this?! - OG}When did I ever ask you to do this?!{Z}{Used as a flashback in Post War 8, at timestamp 31:44}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I just...{Enies 10 - 19:56 (without the "もう")}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:50.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2436)}want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:56.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hilarious! What the heck are they doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:00.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What're you doing?! - OG}What the hell is your problem?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:03.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They risked their lives to come\Nall the way here! - OG}Those guys risked\Nlife and limb to come get you!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:04.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And you... - OG}But you–{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:05.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They did it on their own. - OG}That was their own choice.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:06.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:07.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridic–
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:13.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're in my way. - OG}You're in our way.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:18.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Kaku! Was that in retaliation?! - OG}Blowing off some steam, Kaku?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:20.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You know, for getting that weird fruit? - OG}Is it because you ate such a weird fruit?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:23.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hold your tongue! - OG}Shut your trap!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:24.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I like my fruit! - OG}My fruit is nifty!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:31.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh? Is it just Straw Hat that's our enemy? - OG}Oh? Are we just facing Straw Hat?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:39.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yoyoi! Even if he's alone, it is admirable that he made it this far. - OG}Even if he is alone, it is indeed\Nan impressive feat to have made it this far.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.71,0:17:45.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, yeah. Blueno is down. - OG}No kidding. The guy took out Blueno!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:48.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What a fool! - OG}How crazy is that?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:52.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I guess being a bar owner for five\Nyears would make one weaker, huh? - OG}{Running a bar for five years\Nmust have weakened him, huh? - Z}I guess he lost his edge\Nafter running a bar for five years, huh?{Gaijin/PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:54.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He got so weak that he lost? - OG}He got so rusty that he lost?{Rabbit}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's been defeated. Chapapa. - OG}He went down hard.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:03.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,All right! I'm glad that you're here, CP9!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:05.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,But wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:08.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats have just started imploding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,How could we not watch this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:13.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's freakin' hilarious! - OG}It's prime entertainment!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:27.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Good job, Yokozuna! Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:37.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Guilty...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:39.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:41.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,It's the Guilty Jurors!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:43.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Step aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:46.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We'll pass down the verdict\Nfor that frog's crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:55.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Guilty...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:56.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:12.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.01,0:19:14.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What the heck {\i1}are{\i0} these guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:16.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Guilty! Guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:18.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,No, I mean, go, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:22.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?! Just me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:28.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I never imagined this island\Neven had a chief justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:33.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I thought everyone taken to Enies Lobby\Nwas already considered guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:38.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'd heard they just came here to pass\Nthrough an empty courthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:41.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's wrong, pirates. - OG}You pirates couldn't be more wrong.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:45.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is the most authoritative,\Nfair court in the world. - OG}This is the most authoritative,\Njust court in the world.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:48.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We conduct fair trials!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:49.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:53.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,...the jurors who issue verdicts\Nof guilty or not guilty...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:56.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{are former pirates who're on death row... - OG}are former pirates on death row...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:20:00.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and wish to take you down with them! - OG}who wish to take you down with them!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.52,0:20:06.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Judged by death-row convicts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:09.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hence, in this town, - OG}Hence, no one in this town...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:10.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{no one... - OG}No one!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:13.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{in history has been found not guilty! - OG}...has ever been found not guilty.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:15.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kiwi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.49,0:20:20.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:23.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:25.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:27.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dammit! They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:29.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't give up! - OG}Stand tall!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:33.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If we don't get through here,\Nwe can't bring down the drawbridge! - OG}If we don't get through here,\Nthen we ain't bringing down the drawbridge!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:35.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We left Big Bro's rescue to Straw Hat! - OG}We left Bro's rescue to Straw Hat!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:40.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If we get stuck here,\Nthey can't move forward! - OG}We can't be the ones holding them up here!{arch: This is more literal but it can be reverted if you think OG is much better.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:45.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yokozuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:51.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To think you took so many big iron balls to the face…! - OG}{You seriously took all those\Nbig iron balls to the face! - Z}I can't believe you took\Nall those big iron balls to the face!{Z/PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:53.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:56.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't bother! - OG}You should give up!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:58.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We've still got more than 6,000 soldiers. - OG}We've still got over 6,000 men!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.53,0:21:00.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,All right, everyone into the courthouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:04.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Crush the pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:21.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:23.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Why are the giants...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:24.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Frog!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:27.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:28.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tell me what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:32.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're with Straw Hat-san. - OG}You're with Mr. Straw Hat.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:34.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What the heck is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:38.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To think that he's been holding\Nback this many guards... - OG}Look how many guards he's been holding back!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:41.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That frog is something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:52.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Where the hell are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:55.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They got lost again. - OG}They ran off again.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.09,0:21:56.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We don't have time for this. - OG}We don't have time for this.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:00.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.34,0:22:03.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Basically, so long as I get to the upper floors,\Nit doesn't matter how, right? - OG}{It doesn't matter[/i1]how[/i0]I get\Nto the top floors, right? - Z}It doesn't matter as long as\NI keep heading up, right?{Z/PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.47,0:22:04.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Dragon Twister!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.06,0:22:09.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What?! What's going on?! - OG}Wait! What?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:18.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.83,0:22:33.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You guys really are incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.96,0:22:36.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You even subdued the giants. - OG}You somehow tamed those giants.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.38,0:22:38.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You are a dangerous man! - OG}{You're a pretty dangerous guy! - Z}You're a pretty scary guy!{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.30,0:22:39.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Huh? Er... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:41.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, yeah. - OG}Oh, right!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.97,0:22:44.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All of your friends\Nheaded to the rooftop. - OG}All your friends are headed to the rooftop.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:45.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,The rooftop?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:46.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You should hurry there, too! - OG}You need to go too!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.68,0:22:49.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{King of Snipers. Leave it to me. - OG}{King of Snipers, allow me! - Z}Leave it to me, King of Snipers.{Westfal}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.31,0:22:51.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.69,0:22:57.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You wanna die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.94,0:23:00.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:06.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.16,0:23:09.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If we go over there quickly and eliminate \Nthat guy, wouldn't that end this whole thing? - OG}If we just hop over there and take out\Nthat one guy, all this'll be over, right?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.99,0:23:11.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just wait. - OG}Let's just wait.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:18.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}The captain comes all this way to rescue his crewmate\Njust to have her ultimately refuse his help.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.09,0:23:24.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Have you guys ever seen anything so hilarious? - OG}Have you ever seen something\Nas comical as that?{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:26.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.51,0:23:28.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You wanna die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.51,0:23:32.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Listen to his pathetic shout!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:34.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I can only imagine the look on his...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.81,0:23:38.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What the heck are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.36,0:23:40.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.36,0:23:42.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,H-He's picking his nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.49,0:23:46.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Listen, Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.36,0:23:49.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We've already come this far, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.09,0:24:01.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,we're gonna rescue you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.96,0:24:02.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Nailed it! - OG}Landed!{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.84,0:24:09.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,If you still wanna die after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.26,0:24:11.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{you can die then. - OG}that's your business.{Westfal}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.39,0:24:17.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.56,0:24:19.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.69,0:24:21.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.94,0:24:24.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,But what just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.07,0:24:27.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I have some idea. - OG}I have a hunch.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.79,0:24:39.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I should've come up here\Nlike this from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.33,0:24:40.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.71,0:24:41.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,So it really was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.84,0:24:43.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We were okay because we weren't in the middle of it but if we had been, we would've died! - OG}You're lucky we're alive!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.71,0:24:47.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We were okay because we weren't in the middle of it but if we had been, we would've died! - OG}If we had been right in the middle\Nof it, we would've died!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.05,0:24:48.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Huh? What happened to you guys? - OG}Huh? Did something happen to you guys?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.51,0:24:51.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hiyaa! - OG}Take that!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.05,0:24:52.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.14,0:24:54.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Boar Stew Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.02,0:24:59.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm the first to arrive, without a doubt. - OG}I am, of course, the first to arrive.{Z+arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.27,0:25:01.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Now, I've kept Robin{-chan} waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.27,0:25:02.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'm coming to rescue–
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.69,0:25:04.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Moss!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.07,0:25:07.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Moss Head!\NHow come you got here before me?! - OG}Moss Head! How did you get here before me?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.19,0:25:10.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh? What took you so long?\NDid you get lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.07,0:25:13.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{H-H-Hey, where'd you learn that phrase? - OG}H-H-Hey, hey, hey now, hey!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.20,0:25:16.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't go stealin' that phrase! - OG}Don't go stealing my line!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.46,0:25:21.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sogeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.67,0:25:28.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?! He's flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.34,0:25:30.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.34,0:25:32.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Where's he been all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.02,0:25:40.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Is he... gonna land okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.81,0:25:46.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Whoa… one after another…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.23,0:25:50.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yoyoi! In any case... - OG}At any rate...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.57,0:25:52.86,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Sogeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.86,0:25:55.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{to think that they've marched into headquarters... -OG}...they did march straight into headquarters.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.74,0:26:00.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even though they're our enemy, that's admirable! - OG}{Despite our enmity, their resolve is admirable! - Z}Though they may be our enemy, their resolve is admirable!{Z/PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.79,0:26:06.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A-A-A bunch of pirates have made it this far! - OG}Th-Th-There's that many pirates?!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.86,0:26:29.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm begging you, Robin! - OG}{Hear me out, Robin! - Z}Just hear me out, Robin!{arch: although OG is too strong, he *is* pleading in JP - so I added "just" to reflect that more. "Please, Robin!" (more literal) or "Please hear me out, Robin" would also work but might not fit Luffy.}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.11,0:26:34.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You can go ahead and say you wanna die\Nor whatever, but say those things...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.74,0:26:36.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,by our side!{OG}{when you're with us! - arch: this is tough, maybe workshop in discord if this doesn't work}{Z- With this information, I think the OG ought to do just nicely.}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.58,0:26:40.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's right, Robin-[/i1]chwan[/i0]! - OG}He's right, Robin my love!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.29,0:26:42.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.85,0:27:06.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sogeking. Can you stand up?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.23,0:27:07.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.94,0:27:09.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.73,0:27:12.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,'Tis but a scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.95,0:27:21.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.12,0:28:06.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Just leave the rest to us!{Used as flashback for Enies Lobby 24 @timestamp 20:52}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=13}===============================DIALOGUE============================
